
You can install mappings in 3 modes:

        • normal (default)
        • fullscreen
        • index (≈ command-line ?)

To do so, you need to pass  the optional argument `[fullscreen]` or `[index]` to
the `:map` command. For more info:

        :man zathurarc
        /Mode

Example:

        map  [fullscreen]  f  toggle_fullscreen
